          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-1-1682416382561-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-1-1682416382561-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-1-1682416382561-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Combine your <strong>ground smoked paprika</strong> and <strong>curry powder </strong>with<strong> half</strong> your <strong>natural yoghurt </strong>(you'll use the rest later!) in a bowl</p><p>Add the <strong>chicken breast portions </strong>and <strong>sliced pepper </strong>to the bowl with<strong> </strong>a drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong> and a pinch of<strong> salt </strong>and<strong> pepper </strong>and give everything a good mix up</p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-2-1682416386146-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-2-1682416386146-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-2-1682416386146-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-2-1682416386146-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-2-1682416386146-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>coated chicken breast portions</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong> to a <strong>baking paper</strong>-lined baking tray (or two!)</p><p>Put the tray[s] in the oven for 20-22 min or until the red pepper is slightly charred and the chicken is cooked through (no pink meat!)</p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-3-1682416390560-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
