          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the chicken is in the oven, cut your <strong>green chilli[es]</strong> in quarters lengthways, deseed (scrape the seeds out with a teaspoon) and chop finely</p>",
      "order": 4,
