    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the tandoori chicken is cooked, remove the baking tray[s] from the oven</p><p>Transfer the<strong> tandoori chicken</strong> to a clean board, reserving the tray[s]</p><p>Re-line the reserved baking tray[s] with <strong>baking paper</strong>, add your <strong>plain naans</strong> and top with the <strong>grated cheddar</strong>, <strong>chopped chilli </strong>(can't handle the heat? Go easy!)<strong> </strong>and<strong> charred pepper</strong></p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
